The balloon ride accommodates just two people at a time, in addition to Mr Dewhirst, and is designed for intrepid thrill-seekers.

Passengers must be in ‘moderate’ physical shape and able to complete rigorous fitness and skills training.

The journey is being advertised on Ifonly.com, which offers rare experiences or exclusive products to well-to-do buyers.

